Kaizer Chiefs goalkeeper Itumeleng Khume has reportedly found love in the arms of former Greed &amp; Desire actor Kamo Letsosa. A close source told Sunday Sun that Letsosa was madly in love , but could, however, not say the same about Khune because everyone knows how soccer stars behave .According to the source, it would be a pity if Khune broke her heart she really loved him. The couple, who apparently can t keep their hands off each other, have reportedly been together for three months.Kamo, who is always with Khune s friends, is said to be the right woman for him as she is not a liker of things, like the other girls he has dated . The couple refused to comment on the reports. Meet Khune s new bae:&nbsp;